<body class="bg-dark text-light">

    <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);">
        <h1 class="display-4 text-warning fw-bold mb-5">About the Algorithm</h1>

        <div class="card bg-dark border-light shadow-lg text-light" style="max-width: 800px;">
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
                    The <span class="text-warning fw-bold">Base62 algorithm</span> was chosen for generating short URLs due to its
                    efficiency and compactness. Base62 utilizes digits, uppercase, and lowercase letters
                    (<code>0-9</code>, <code>A-Z</code>, and <code>a-z</code>), creating short and easily readable links.
                </p>
                <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
                    Each URL is transformed from a numerical identifier into a string using this base-62 numeral system,
                    ensuring uniqueness. By encoding the record ID rather than the original URL,
                    every shortened link remains unique.
                </p>
                <p class="fs-5 mb-0">
                    This approach provides an optimal balance between simplicity and performance in URL shortening systems.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

